   "description":"IR8A form Singapore — what it is, what to include, the March 1 deadline, Auto Inclusion Scheme obligations, and how to avoid the most common employer filing errors.",
   "url":"https://accountantforsmallbusiness.com/blog/ir8a-form-singapore-employer-guide/",
   "datePublished":"2026-06-29","dateModified":"2026-06-29","inLanguage":"en-SG",
   "image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://accountantforsmallbusiness.com/hero-bg.jpg","width":1200,"height":630},
   "author":{"@id":"https://accountantforsmallbusiness.com/#mehdi"},
